data.description: 4% Interest Rate with the Assumable Mortgage!!! ***TWO LEGAL PARCELS*** You've struck GOLD! This property includes an additional building lot. Enjoy the extra space or build another dwelling, ADU, shop, etc. The home is 5 Bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms, and 2200+ Square Foot including plenty of space with the Dining Room AND Formal Dining Room/flex space in addition to the two great rooms! Relax in the Hot Tub on the back patio. ZIP on the Zip Line, or enjoy the outdoor fire pit which is great for entertaining. Plenty of room for storage in the additional storage shed. Fresh and NEW Exterior Paint on the home. Conveniently located and within walking distance to the green belt taking you to all things great in Idaho City - shopping, restaurants and amenities. Enjoy the fishing ponds in Mores Creek Sub and State Land access close by. You won't want to miss out on this turn key ready home!
